 \{ans_rule(15)\}\( \mathbf{j}+\) \{ans_rule(15)\} \( {\mathbf{k}}\) $BR
 
 and \( \int{\mathbf{r}}(t)\, dt \)= \{ans_rule(15)\} \( \mathbf{i}+\)
